@startuml
!theme plain
hide footbox
autonumber

actor "APP" as APP
participant "Middleware" as MW
participant "Banco de Comercio" as BDC

title 01) POST /bdc/auth
APP -> MW: POST /bdc/auth
MW -> BDC: POST /auth
BDC --> MW: accessToken / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

newpage
title 02) GET /bdc/healthcheck
APP -> MW: GET /bdc/healthcheck
MW -> BDC: GET /healthcheck
BDC --> MW: estado servicio / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 503 / 500

newpage
title 03) GET /bdc/accounts?token=<JWT_APP>
APP -> MW: GET /bdc/accounts?token=...
MW -> MW: Validar JWT APP
MW -> BDC: GET /accounts
BDC --> MW: cuentas / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

newpage
title 04) GET /bdc/accounts/info/{cbu_cvu_alias}?token=<JWT_APP>
APP -> MW: GET /bdc/accounts/info/{id}?token=...
MW -> MW: Validar JWT APP
MW -> BDC: GET /accounts/info/{id}
BDC --> MW: info cuenta / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

newpage
title 05) POST /bdc/accounts/get-cvu-accounts?token=<JWT_APP>
APP -> MW: POST /bdc/accounts/get-cvu-accounts
MW -> MW: Validar JWT APP
MW -> MW: Calcular X-SIGNATURE
MW -> BDC: POST /accounts/get-cvu-accounts
note right of MW
Headers: Authorization + X-SIGNATURE
end note
BDC --> MW: listado subcuentas / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

newpage
title 06) POST /bdc/sub-account?token=<JWT_APP>&tipo=...
APP -> MW: POST /bdc/sub-account?tipo=empresa|p2p
MW -> MW: Validar JWT APP
MW -> MW: Generar alias/originId y firma
MW -> BDC: POST /sub-account
BDC --> MW: subcuenta creada / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

newpage
title 07) GET /bdc/sub-account/{origin_id}?token=<JWT_APP>
APP -> MW: GET /bdc/sub-account/{origin_id}
MW -> MW: Validar JWT APP
MW -> BDC: GET /sub-account/{origin_id}
BDC --> MW: detalle subcuenta / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

newpage
title 08) PATCH /bdc/sub-account/{cvu}?token=<JWT_APP>
APP -> MW: PATCH /bdc/sub-account/{cvu}
MW -> MW: Validar JWT APP
MW -> MW: Calcular X-SIGNATURE
MW -> BDC: PATCH /sub-account/{cvu}
BDC --> MW: subcuenta actualizada / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

newpage
title 09) POST /bdc/movements/{cbu_cvu_alias}?token=<JWT_APP>
APP -> MW: POST /bdc/movements/{id}
MW -> MW: Validar JWT APP
MW -> MW: Calcular X-SIGNATURE
MW -> BDC: POST /movements/{id}
BDC --> MW: movimientos / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

newpage
title 10) POST /bdc/global/data/get-entity?token=<JWT_APP>
APP -> MW: POST /bdc/global/data/get-entity
MW -> MW: Validar JWT APP
MW -> MW: Calcular X-SIGNATURE
MW -> BDC: POST /global/data/get-entity
BDC --> MW: datos entidad / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

newpage
title 11) POST /bdc/apiV1/ultimosMovimientos?token=<JWT_APP>
APP -> MW: POST /bdc/apiV1/ultimosMovimientos
MW -> MW: Validar JWT APP
MW -> BDC: POST /apiV1/ultimosMovimientos
BDC --> MW: ultimos movimientos / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

newpage
title 12) POST /bdc/transfer-request?token=<JWT_APP>
APP -> MW: POST /bdc/transfer-request
MW -> MW: Validar JWT APP y saldo
MW -> BDC: GET /accounts/info/{destinationCbuCvu}
BDC --> MW: datos cuenta destino / error
MW -> MW: Calcular X-SIGNATURE
MW -> BDC: POST /movements/transfer-request
BDC --> MW: transferencia creada / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

newpage
title 13) GET /bdc/movements/transfer-request/{origin_id}?token=<JWT_APP>
APP -> MW: GET /bdc/movements/transfer-request/{origin_id}
MW -> MW: Validar JWT APP
MW -> BDC: GET /movements/transfer-request/{origin_id}
BDC --> MW: estado transferencia / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

newpage
title 14) GET /bdc/snp-concepts?token=<JWT_APP>
APP -> MW: GET /bdc/snp-concepts
MW -> MW: Validar JWT APP
MW -> BDC: GET /get-snp-concepts
BDC --> MW: conceptos SNP / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

newpage
title 15) POST /bdc/alias?token=<JWT_APP>
APP -> MW: POST /bdc/alias
MW -> MW: Validar JWT APP
MW -> MW: Calcular X-SIGNATURE
MW -> BDC: POST /alias
BDC --> MW: lookup alias / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

newpage
title 16) POST /bdc/alias-create?token=<JWT_APP>
APP -> MW: POST /bdc/alias-create
MW -> MW: Validar JWT APP
MW -> MW: Calcular X-SIGNATURE
MW -> BDC: POST /alias-create
BDC --> MW: alias creado / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

newpage
title 17) PATCH /bdc/alias-edit?token=<JWT_APP>
APP -> MW: PATCH /bdc/alias-edit
MW -> MW: Validar JWT APP y payload
MW -> MW: Calcular X-SIGNATURE
MW -> BDC: POST /alias-edit
BDC --> MW: alias editado / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

newpage
title 18) POST /bdc/alias-remove?token=<JWT_APP>
APP -> MW: POST /bdc/alias-remove
MW -> MW: Validar JWT APP
MW -> MW: Calcular X-SIGNATURE
MW -> BDC: POST /alias-remove
BDC --> MW: alias eliminado / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 4xx / 5xx

newpage
title 19) GET /bdc/auth/status (debug)
APP -> MW: GET /bdc/auth/status
MW -> MW: Validar Authorization Bearer (JWT APP)
MW -> MW: Leer estado cache token BDC
note over BDC
Sin llamada externa al banco
end note
MW --> APP: 200 estado autenticación

newpage
title 20) POST /bdc/auth/refresh (debug)
APP -> MW: POST /bdc/auth/refresh
MW -> MW: Validar Authorization Bearer (JWT APP)
MW -> MW: Invalidar cache token BDC
MW -> BDC: POST /auth
BDC --> MW: token renovado / error
MW --> APP: 200 / 500

@enduml
